window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>To end the wraith threat, the dimensional barrier must be healed.</p> <p>But to do that, Charles will need to find a way back to Earth again! Only then can a combination of magic and technology repair the damage his arrival in Kortall caused.</p> <p>The quest to return to Earth is only the beginning of his troubles.</p> <p>Because the wraiths have been very busy, and not just in Kortall. They've invaded Earth as well!</p> <p>Smith quickly finds himself embroiled in two wars on two worlds against an implacable foe determined to spread across the multiverse until all life is devoured.</p> <p>If he can't stop them, it could well mean the end of . . . everything.</p>"; 
